R. E. ALLEN, as Receiver, etc., v. Robert E. CLARK, United States Marshal, etc., et al. No. 9123. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. March 23, 1939. William C. Ring, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellant. Irl D. Brett, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellees.

Before GARRECHT, HANEY, and STEPHENS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for respective parties, and good cause therefor appearing, ordered appeal in above cause dismissed, that a decree of dismissal be filed and entered pursuant to stipulation, and that the mandate of this court in this cause issue forthwith.
